(30, 4, '30_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Monster Mania Dino Egg Hunt', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.MonsterMania'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width="100"><br></td>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/monster-mania-dino-egg-hunt/id876620356'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/app_store_en.png" height="120" width="347"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Monster Mania Dino Egg Hunt is an addicting smasher game whose main objective is to slice through as many eggs as possible by slashing through them with your finger similarly to the hottest android games of all time - Cookie Monster Ninja. Join the game and become the ultimate dino egg smasher with each and every single swipe of your claw. Don''t wait any longer and downlaod this splendid game and help to feed our clumsy little monster. He not only loves eggs, but cookies as well.<br><br>To keep players entertained and thrilled, the game offers four unique and different game modes, which include: Classic, Arcade, Rush, and Tap. Undoubtedly, these four amazing, action-packed levels will keep you amused for many hours. Apart from them, the game has to offer many hidden levels, bonuses, combos, achievements and many more. Join this epic adventure now and say no to boredom. This game is a simple and fun, yet brilliant, mini game, an awesome time killer.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/3KxfjgzTA54" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nKey features:<br><br>- Slice your way through tons of colourful cartoon-looking cookies and eggs<br>while avoiding bombs at all cost<br>- Free to play<br>- Easiest game to pick up<br>- Colourful and vivid graphics<br>- Amazing slasher sound effects<br>- Four action-packed game modes, which make the gameplay even more exciting: Classic, Arcade, Rush, Tap<br>- Enriched gameplay with astonishing power-ups, cookies, explosions, bonuses, combos, hidden <br>levels<br><br>Monster Mania Dino Egg Hunt is an old-school, and almost as good and hot as the original Cookie Ninja, slasher on Android which in combination with addictive gameplay guarantess hours of fun.<br></p>', 1),
(31, 4, '31_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Penguin Quest Antarctica Adventure', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.PenguinQuestFREE'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width="100"><br></td>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/clumsy-penguin-quest-ice-saga/id876485515'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/app_store_en.png" height="120" width="347"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Far, far away in a remote continent called Antarctica lives Pokey, a tiny and quite little penguin, along with his girlfriend penguin. Unfortunately, one day evil bears and wolves sneaked into his igloo and kidnapped his girlfriend along with all the fish stored for the upcoming icy winter. Are you willing to help Pokey the penguin in his epic quest of retrieving his beloved one along with the fish?<br><br>Penguin Quest - Antarctica Adventure is 2014 app is a game whose main objective is to help little funny penguin get to a piece of ice flow where his beloved one along with the pirate treasure chest is located to colpete a level. Moreover, it is also very important to collect as many fish as possible along your journey. Join this marvelous puzzle game now and discover many individually designed levels to be figured out. In this straightforward, yet enjoyable, mini adventure.<br><br>How to play:<br><br>Upon entering a level you will see objects coloured in gray. Before being able to interact with the said objects, you have to tap them to make them unlocked. Tip: you can lock and unlock any items as many times as you want to. It is very helpful in overcoming certain complex levels. After unlocking the penguin your main objective is to get him to the piece of ice with his girlfriend and pirate chest on it. Possible object to unlock: penguin, ice blocks, rope with ice ball attached to it, clouds, etc.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/gJ83DUSMbUo" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nDo you feel a chill?<br><br>Key features:<br><br>- Discover lots of completely unique levels<br>- Help our adorable penguin character find its way to the pirate chest<br>- Awesome hand-drawn graphics<br>- Complex and innovative game physics<br>- Addictive gameplay<br><br>Come and join the fun with the cute and adorable Pokey the angry penguin.<br></p>', 1),
(32, 4, '32_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Atlantis Gem Smash', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.AtlantisGemSmash'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>We bring you more than just precious stones, we bring you an ancient Atlantean power.<br><br>Atlantis Gem Smash is a fast paced game whose main objective is to tap the falling jewels to destroy them. It''s based on the concept of the ancient culture of forgotten kingdom of Atlantis.<br><br>The destruction of jewels happens only when there are at least 3 gems of the same type nearby. The game is an epic<br>time killer with stunning graphics, effects that include bombs, explosions, beautiful scenery and UI, and great sound effects and was designed with all diamond games lovers in mind. If you like smashing all sorts of diamonds, gems and jewels, you will certainly enjoy this epic mini game.<br><br>How to play:<br>1. Match at least 3 or more jewels of the same type to smash them and get points that will unlock many achievements.<br>2. Smash as fast and as many jewels as you can to avoid getting them stack up and making you lose the game.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/UxL0Nd0FSUw" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nFeatures:<br>- more than 50 levels with increasing difficulty, achievements and types of diamonds, jewels, and gems<br>- more than 10 extra items (bombs, arrows, etc.) helping you in the destruction of jewels<br>- 30 various achievements to be unlocked<br>- beautiful background including forests, caves, statues,and remainings of the Atlantean architecture.<br>- tons of fun in a short amount of time<br><br>Don''t hesitate and join now this epic jewel adventure. This game is like a delicious and sweet candy, leading to an instant addiction. Become the hero, an absolute legend, of the gem collection scene. This game is something much greater than just a diamond dash. Join this epic jewel adventure as it is a true blitz. Forget about being a gold digger and become the greates diamond smasher there has ever been in the entire scene. Dont wait any longer! Just hit the downlad button and get this amazing free jewels game now !<br></p>', 1),
(33, 4, '33_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Bubbly Bubbles', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.BubblyBubbles'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Bubbly Bubbles - Gem Pop Madness is a classic bubble shooter game that can be picked up by both kids and adults. Just match 3 gems of the same type (there are 6 different jewels types in total) to make them burst. Try to blast as many as you can in one shot to set your score literally on blaze. Remember also that time is your ally thus try to be swift with the jewel match to get the multipliers that will double or even tripple your score. To clear a level you have to clash all the gem bubbles.<br><br>Amazing Graphics and Sounds:<br>Let your eyes and ears enjoy on Bubble Bubbles dazzling HD graphics and high, crystal clear, sounds. Experience this gem shooter in an obsolutely new dimension.<br><br>Don''t wait any longer and download this blitz kicking game today and join this dazzling quest. Moreover, this game is perfect for people of all ages as it teaches not only fast thinking, but also requires good eye to hand coordination. So stop wasting your time and start putting those bubbles on blaze.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/hEM-qFtVi00" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nHow to Play:<br>Just swipe your finger on the screen or tap the direction in which you want the jewels to be fired. You can also bounce the balls off the wall. Look at the arrow for the extra assistance. Be quick to burst burst the bubbles before the metal slab reaches the botton and crushes your finger.<br><br>Key Features:<br>- Classic bubble shooter with a more mature approach<br>- Easy to play - just match 3 gems of the same type to blast<br>- Limitless levels and fun<br>- Addicting gameplay<br>- One of the few bubble shooters supporting horizontal view Ă˘ÂÂ pure madness<br>- Free to play<br></p>', 1),
(34, 4, '34_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Elite Classic Chess', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.EliteClassicChessFree'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Elite Classic Chess FREE is based on a well-known chess board game. The game was designed in a manner to retain this classic feeling of chess through a realistically looking chessboard and chess pieces, as well as simplified and intuitive user interface. Moreover, players might choose from one of three difficulty levels with an AI able to learn and adapt to a variety of strategies.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/82uBMz7RhbM" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nKey features:<br><br>- 3 levels of difficulty (easy, normal, hard)<br>- Based on a greatly improved Treebeard Chess Engine used in MSN Chess by Microsoft, which results super intelligent, almost human-like AI intelligence and adaptability<br>- Minimalistic and intuitive UI <br>- Colourful and vivid graphics <br></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `nta_article` (`id`, `id_grid`, `photo`, `date`, `title`, `information`, `online`) VALUES
(35, 4, '35_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Happy Bunny', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;">\r\n              <tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.HappyBunnyFREE'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width="100"><br></td>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/happy-bunny-super-forest-jump/id883786045'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/app_store_en.png" height="120" width="347"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Happy Bunny: Pocket Jump Saga revolves around the story of a very cheerful pet. Somewhere deep in a valley covered with all types of plants lies a forest in which lives Justin, a tiny, yet brave, bunny. Unfortunately, one day as he was collecting carrots, he lost his way back home, when a dumb hedgehog thief stole his map, as the hungry rabbit was about to pick up some delicious plants from the nearest farm. Now he''s all alone like a tiny dot in the middle of dark woods. Are you brave enough to help Justin in his epic voyage of finding the way back home even against all the elements? Splendid, now stop wasting your time and join this epic voyage that will transform the main pet from zero to hero.<br><br>Happy Bunny: Pocket Jump Saga is a game whose main objective is to help a tinny bunny find a way back home by crossing door frontier after solving hard puzzles and overcoming the elements. In order to get to the door with the key, you will have to jump, sometimes, dash, or even roll over the platforms or even break some bricks. However, if you fail to get to another platform you will end up dead falling down and getting eaten alive by nasty worms. Moreover, it is also very important to collect as many plants, but mainly carrots, as possible, so the pet doesn''t stay hungry along the voyage. Join this greately enhanced puzzle game now and discover many individually designed levels to be solved in this straightforward, yet enjoyable, tiny voyage.<br><br>How to play:<br><br>Before being able to interact with the bricks and platforms, you have to tap them to make them unlocked or force them to drop on the land and break. Tip: you can lock and unlock any items as many times as you want to. It is very helpful in solving especially complex levels. After unlocking the tiny bunny your main objective is to get him to the door and escape the valley forest.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/PbL5qbfHd7Q" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nKey features:<br><br>- Discover lots of completely unique levels<br>- Colourful and vivid graphics<br>- Splendid high quality sound effects and music<br>- Game play designed for all age groups (kids / teenagers / adults)<br>- Cute pet bunny waiting to be looked after<br>- Enhanced and innovative game physics and puzzles<br>- Addictive gameplay<br><br>Now dash to the store and mash that download button to embark on the magnificent voyage presented to you in the Pocket Jump Saga of Happy Bunny.<br></p>', 1),
(36, 4, '36_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Booty of Cleopatra', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;"><tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.BootyOfCleopatra'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>                \r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Somewhere deep in the desert, among the golden sands of oblivion, lies an ancient pyramid, a tomb build centuries ago during the time of arabian nights to pay respects to the one and only Queen of Nile, Cleopatra, and the Egyptian God of Sun - Ra. As with every vaults, this pyramid tomb has unmeasured riches hidden in its deepest corners. In this game you become a thief that tries to get in to the highest levels of the pyramid to loot all the booty within, among which there are gems, ancient swords, gold chests and many more other valuables. <br><br>The main objective of the Booty of Cleopatra - Loot Flow is to play as a novice thief who tries to find a way to break in to the treasure room of the queen''s of the Nile pyramid in this match symbol game. In order to get to the next level you will have to fight against the clock and just follow the flow of matching appropriate symbols. However, you will have to be really swift to make it in the given time. Moreover, mindless swiping wont make you go too far later in the game since you want to get the flow going as long as possible.<br><br>How to play:<br>Choose the first level from the list and then just swipe your finger to keep the flow of the same items going. So the game incorporates the idea of a match 3 game as well. Remember that you need to swipe over at least 3 symbols of the same type to get it removed. Furthermore, it is essential to to match as many items as possible as it will give you bonus points, achievements and increase your time. As you progress, the game will keep adding new symbols to be matched, making it even harder to make it in the given time thus forcing the players to choose carefuly the items, so they get most out of their decisions.<br><br>Key features:<br><br>- Discover almost 50 levels<br>- Colourful and vivid graphics<br>- Splendid high quality sound effects and music<br>- Game play designed for all age groups (kids / teenagers / adults)<br>- Addictive gameplay<br><br>Now dash to the store and mash that download button to embark on the magnificent voyage presented to you in the Booty of Cleopatra - Loot Flow.<br></p>', 1),
(37, 4, '37_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Draw the Rope Doodle Ballies', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;"><tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.DrawtheRopeFREE'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width="100"><br></td>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/draw-the-rope-doodle-ballies/id845558927'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/app_store_en.png" height="120" width="347"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Draw the rope to help little funny doodle balls get into the refreshing water on this how warm summer day. Join this marvelous puzzle game now and discover many individually designed levels to be figured out. In this straightforward, yet enjoyable, mini adventure, the player is supposed to detonate a wooden beam to realease cute balls that will then slide down the previously drawn rope into the wooden basket filled with water. Be a good guy and help the ballies.<br><br>Remember this game is all about collecting gold starts, discovering bonuses, collecting as much points as possible, unlocking completely new levels that will provide you with new challenges in this how addictive, physics-based mini game. Join the adventure presented to by what could be the best and hottest android app of summer. <br><br>Don''t cut the rope just draw it and become your own drawing god!\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/QEXz7e8jJIw" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nKey features:<br>- Discover lots of completely unique levels<br>- Help our adorable characters find their way down<br>- Awesome hand-drawn graphics<br>- Complex and innovative game physics<br>- Addictive gameplay<br>- Doodle feel of the game<br><br>Come join the fun with the balls.<br></p>', 1),
(38, 4, '38_a.jpg', '2014-11-19', 'Diamond Bird Night Flight', '<table style="margin:20px auto 20px auto;"><tbody><tr>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.invedion.DiamondBirdNightRun'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/google_play_en.png" height="120" width="405"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width="100"><br></td>\r\n                <td align="center">\r\n                <a href="#" onclick="navigator.app.loadUrl(''https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/diamond-bird-night-run/id851980303'', {openExternal : true});" target="_blank"><img src="images/app_store_en.png" height="120" width="347"></a>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p>Diamond Phoenix Gem Flight is a physics flight simulator game that takes place somewhere high in the highest sky where, Twerky, a tiny gem bird lives. Unfortunately, the sweet little creature, similarly to other birds, cannot resist the beauty of shiny jewels. Will you be brave enough to accept the challenge and help out our bird thief as he''s flying, trying to escape the raging storm at night during his quest to collect all the precious diamonds floating in the sky? Join this epic adventure now and achieve great victory or fall down from the sky bursting into flames like Icarus himself, but beware this game has been set to the hardest difficulty possible!<br><br>How to play?<br><br>Just tap on the screen of your device to make the main protagonist, diamond bird, flap his wings and fly up. However, don''t tap mindlessly as you will soon end up being nothing more, but a crispy chicken once you hit the electric pipes and get electrocuted during this crazy flight quest. To make the challenge more demanding, the obstacles, which in this case are lightning pipes, are constantly moving up and down. On top of that, a player has to collect jewels that will give them extra free points and help unlock new achievements and best their friends high score. Remember that whenever you fly through the pipes, you get awarded with 1 point, but if you manage to get a diamond you will also get another 10 points for taking the extra risk.<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/3mq5Msriyho" frameborder="0" height="557" width="990"></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nKey features:<br>- Addictive, yet simple, game play<br>- Cartoon feel with amazing music<br>- Beautiful design<br>- Tons of fun<br>- Easy controls - just tap to flap your wings<br>- Everything that makes a mobile game awesome, namely a cute bird, humor, and jewels<br>- Advance flight physics mimicking the natural gravity of the Earth<br>- Developed with hardest difficulty in mind<br>- Free to play<br><br>If you are really into cartoon games, you will undoubtedly love this game. Especially, that similarly to other great online games this one has been developed with the use of Adobe Air. So if you fancy Flash games, you''re surely going to feel at home. Moreover, this game is perfect for children, not only because they love cute and tiny birds. but also because the game helps in improving their reflexes and fast thinking.<br><br>Don''t waste any more time and download this epic game for free on your phone and start flapping those wings, buddy!<br><br>If you like our Diamond Phoenix Gem Flight and would like to support us, feel free to visit our facebook profile.<br></p>', 1),
